
Feature functions

FinalRhymeModel          - rhyming words at the end of each sentence
SentenceInitialCharModel - identical initial characters for each sentence
WordInitalCharModel      - identical initial characters for each word


Config files

de-en.rhyme.ini - FinalRhymeModel
de-en.initial.ini - SentenceInitialCharModel
de-en.initial-char.ini - WordInitialCharModel



NOTES

suffix array implementation:
